title: V11 — Non-Player Characters (NPCs)
story: familyzoo
entry: v11
author: Sharpee Tutorial
description: Verify zookeeper patrol behavior and parrot NPC in the aviary

---

# V11 teaches: NPCs with NpcTrait, NpcPlugin, patrol and custom behaviors

# The player starts at the Zoo Entrance
> look
[OK: contains "Zoo Entrance"]

# Go south to Main Path — the zookeeper starts here
> south
[OK: contains "Main Path"]

# The zookeeper should be visible in the room
> examine zookeeper
[OK: contains "khaki overalls"]
[OK: contains "Sam"]

# Go west to the Aviary — the parrot lives here
> west
[OK: contains "Aviary"]

# The parrot should be visible
> examine parrot
[OK: contains "scarlet macaw"]
[OK: contains "bright eye"]

# Wait a few turns — the parrot may speak (behavior is random)
# We just confirm the wait command works without errors
> wait
[OK: contains "Time passes"]

> wait
[OK: contains "Time passes"]

# Go back east to Main Path
> east
[OK: contains "Main Path"]
